OL,3,CTrain firm names 11 schools with
OL,4,Ctrouble-making students
OL,6,FTrain operator Northern has written to
OL,7,Fthe headteachers of 11 secondary
OL,8,Fschools calling for help to stop
OL,9,F"persistent, calculated" fare dodging.
OL,11,FThe company said there had been a
OL,12,Fcatalogue of incidents since September
OL,13,F2023, including students travelling
OL,14,Fwithout tickets, ticket fraud and anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour as well as verbal and
OL,16,Fphysical assaults on conductors and
OL,17,Fstation staff.
OL,19,FBehaviour at some stations has been so
OL,20,Fbad that it has had to call on help
OL,21,Ffrom British Transport Police.
