OL,6,FThe 11 schools are:
OL,8,FMark Powles, commercial and customer
OL,9,Fdirector at Northern, said: "What
OL,10,Fwe're seeing is persistent, calculated
OL,11,Ffare evasion.
OL,13,F"With secondary school students, fare
OL,14,Fevasion incidents tend to occur on
OL,15,Frelatively short journeys between
OL,16,Frural and suburban stations which are
OL,17,Fnot barrier-controlled.
