OL,6,F"That, combined with the limited time
OL,7,Fconductors have to carry out ticket
OL,8,Fchecks, emboldens students to travel
OL,9,Fwithout a ticket."
OL,11,FIn recent months, Northern said
OL,12,Fincidents had escalated.
OL,14,F"We've seen students climb on station
OL,15,Fcanopies and assault station staff in
OL,16,Forder to avoid ticket checks - it's
OL,17,Fcompletely unacceptable," Mr Powles
OL,18,Fadded.
