OL,4,Ctrouble-making students
OL,6,F"That's why we're calling on
OL,7,Fheadteachers to help us identify
OL,8,Frepeat offenders."
OL,10,FThe train operator is already working
OL,11,Fwith Honley High School in West
OL,12,FYorkshire and says a "joined-up
OL,13,Fapproach" makes a difference.
OL,15,FTeachers have been sent to Honley
OL,16,Fstation to help identify students and
OL,17,Fensure station staff are able to carry
OL,18,Fout ticket checks without a risk to
OL,19,Ftheir safety.
