OL,6,FJames Meads, the assistant headteacher
OL,7,Fof Honley High School, said: "As well
OL,8,Fas raising the topic of fare evasion
OL,9,Fin school assemblies, we have also
OL,10,Fcontacted the parents of students to
OL,11,Fmake them aware - and we will continue
OL,12,Fto support Northern on this issue when
OL,13,Fthe new academic year gets underway in
OL,14,FSeptember."
OL,16,FNorthern is now in talks with
OL,17,FHighfields College and Sutton Academy
OL,18,Fto adopt a similar approach at their
OL,19,Flocal stations from September.
